import Layout from '../components/layout'
import Menu from '../components/Menu'
import RadarChart from '../components/RadarChart'
const { Row, Col  } = Reactstrap

function Home() {
    return (
      <Layout>
        <header>
          <Row>
              <Col sm="12" md="12" lg="12">
                <Menu></Menu>
              </Col>
          </Row>
        </header>
        <RadarChart></RadarChart>
      </Layout>
    )
}

export default Home
